com.prc.alp.liaison.interact
Interface CloneableInteractor

All Known Implementing Classes:
CoABSDefaultInteractor, RETSINAUnexpectedWxInteractor
public interface CloneableInteractor
extends MultithreadInteractor, java.lang.Cloneable

An interactor that can safely clone itself on demand. This may be required by some InteractionFactory specializations that use a non-shareable interactor (i.e., an interactor that maintains some distinct internal state and cannot therefore be shared among separate interactions).
